projects.name: Travel Website
projects.description: Developed a responsive travel website utilizing HTML, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript, featuring sections for home, about, packages, and booking functionalities. Implemented backend functionality using PHP and MySQL for dynamic content management and user booking interaction. Ensured cross-device compatibility and user accessibility through responsive design techniques.

projects.name: Allyers: AI Mental Health Assistant
projects.description: Contributed by working in a team of three members in developing Allyers, a mental wellness platform that utilizes AI to provide personalised mental health support, suggestions and consultations. Allyers ChatBuddy allows to input prompts, provide text-based responses, and have them read aloud using voice conversion technology. Utilized the layout editor to create a UI for the application in order to allow different scenes to interact with each other.

projects.name: Tic Tac Toe Game
projects.description: Developed an interactive Tic Tac Toe game using React.js with useState and useEffect hooks for dynamic UI and state management. Implemented a modular component-based architecture for maintainable and reusable code. Enhanced user experience with JavaScript audio for gameplay sound effects and a responsive design using CSS flex-box and grid. Ensured cross-device compatibility and accessibility through responsive design principles.
